<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="ja">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>
        PonPon.SE
    </title>
    <meta content="タイトル" name="title">
    <meta content="ディスクリプション" name="description">
    <meta content="キーワード" name="keywords">
    <link href="" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- フォントの初期設定 -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@100;300;400;500;700;900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        html {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
    </style>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='./stylesheets/style.css' />
    <!-- jquery -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <!-- font-awesome -->
	<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/03ebcee952.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <main>
        <h1 class="dn">ポン出しアプリ「PonPon.SE」</h1>
        <article class="p_modal-soundAttention l_modal" id="enter_modal">
            <div class="p_modal-soundAttention__wrapper">
                <h2 class="p_modal-soundAttention__h2 mb40">Welcome to "<span class="p_modal-soundAttention__span">PonPon.SE</span>"</h2>
                <div class="p_modal-soundAttention__contents-wrapper mb20">
                    <div class="p_modal-soundAttention__iconWrapper"><i class="fas fa-volume-up p_modal-soundAttention__icon"></i></div>
                    <p>このサイトでは音声が流れます。<br>スピーカーの音量にご注意ください。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p_modal-soundAttention__btn-wrapper">
                    <div class="c_btn_side_round c_btn_side_round--black l_inlineBlock-center" id="enter">ENTER</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article id="main" class="l_contents">
            <section class="l_contents__nav">
                <div class="p_se_nav__logo-wrapper">
                    <h2 class="p_se_nav__logo">PonPon.SE</h2>
                    <p class="p_se_nav__version">ver1.0</p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="l_contents__main">
                <ul class="p_pad-area">
                    <li class="p_pad-area__btn--nomal p_pad-area__btn">
                        <i class="fas fa-music p_pad-area__icon--nomal p_pad-area__icon"></i>
                        <p class="p_pad-area__title--nomal p_pad-area__title">アジト</p>
                        <i class="fas fa-play p_pad-area__play--nomal p_pad-area__play"></i>
                        <p class="p_pad-area__time--nomal p_pad-area__time"><span></span><span class="sound_duration"></span></p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="p_pad-area__btn--nomal p_pad-area__btn">
                        <i class="fas fa-music p_pad-area__icon--nomal p_pad-area__icon"></i>
                        <p class="p_pad-area__title--nomal p_pad-area__title">ハンター試験からの脱出</p>
                        <i class="fas fa-play p_pad-area__play--nomal p_pad-area__play"></i>
                        <p class="p_pad-area__time--nomal p_pad-area__time"><span></span><span class="sound_duration"></span></p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="p_pad-area__btn--nomal p_pad-area__btn">
                        <i class="fas fa-music p_pad-area__icon--nomal p_pad-area__icon"></i>
                        <p class="p_pad-area__title--nomal p_pad-area__title">KOTOKOTO</p>
                        <i class="fas fa-play p_pad-area__play--nomal p_pad-area__play"></i>
                        <p class="p_pad-area__time--nomal p_pad-area__time"><span></span><span class="sound_duration"></span></p>
                    </li>
                    <div class="p_pad-area__stop-btn" id="stop_button">
                        停止
                    </div>
            </section>
        </article>
        <ul>
            <li><audio src="./audio/bgm/azito.mp3" class="ponpon_audio" loop></audio></li>
            <li><audio src="./audio/bgm/escape from hunter test.mp3" class="ponpon_audio" loop></audio></li>
            <li><audio src="./audio/bgm/kotokoto.mp3" class="ponpon_audio" loop></audio></li>
        </ul>
    </main> 
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/socket.io/4.2.0/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="/javascripts/ponpon_se.js"></script>
</body>

</html>